      <title>分析师称中国人民银行对债券市场的打击将收效甚微</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/pboc-salvo-on-bond-rally-may-have-limited-impact-analysts-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管央行准备出售数千亿元人民币的债券以冷却股市上涨，但中国观察人士对央行影响收益率下行压力的能力仍表示怀疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/pboc-salvo-on-bond-rally-may-have-limited-impact-analysts-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 03:04:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
